document.title: Dictionary of the Brabant Dialects
document.intro: The Dictionary of Brabantic Dialects (WBD) covers together with the Dictionary of the Limburgian Dialects (WLD) and the Dictionary of the Flemish dialects (WVD) by a same type of descriptive dialect lexicography the entire Southern Dutch ­speaking region below the major rivers. This are... Part III (General Vocabulary): Subcollections WBD Part I: Agricultural vocabulary WBD Part II: Non-Agricultural vocabulary
